  "title": "Intro to Video Review &#8211; Using PlaySight and Squashskills to improve your game",
  "excerpt": "We have limited spots (about 1/week) available for 1-on-1 and small group sessions to learn how to use the PlaySight video review system to review your game. The sessions are provided free to any member or trial-member of the Edmonton Squash Club. Sessions include: A discussion of common technical flaws that are correctible with video &#8230; Read more",
  "content": "\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">We have limited spots (about 1/week) available for 1-on-1 and small group sessions to learn how to use the PlaySight video review system to review your game. The sessions are provided free to any member or trial-member of the Edmonton Squash Club.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Sessions include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ol class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>A discussion of common technical flaws that are correctible with video review</li><li>An introduction to the PlaySight video review system</li><li>An on-court session tailored to the participants skill level</li><li>Session review using the desktop PlaySight station</li><li>Comparison and suggestions for improvement using Squashskills.com videos as a reference</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">The session is run by Sean Peacock who coordinated the install of the PlaySight system when then club was opened. </p>\n\n\n\n                <div class='gf_browser_unknown gform_wrapper gform_legacy_markup_wrapper gform-theme--no-framework' data-form-theme='legacy' data-form-index='0' id='gform_wrapper_84' >\n                        <div class='gform_heading'>\n                            <h3 class=\"gform_title\">PlaySight Course</h3>\n                            <p class='gform_description'>Request for a PlaySight Instructional Session</p>\n                        </div><form method='post' enctype='multipart/form-data'  id='gform_84'  action='/wp-json/wp/v2/posts?per_page=100&#038;page=1&#038;status=publish' data-formid='84' novalidate>\n                        <div class='gform-body gform_body'><ul id='gform_fields_84' class='gform_fields top_label form_sublabel_below description_below validation_below'><li id=\"field_84_1\" class=\"gfield gfield--type-name field_sublabel_below gfield--no-description field_description_below field_validation_below gfield_visibility_visible\"  ><label class='gfield_label gform-field-label gfield_label_before_complex' >Name</label><div